UK ' s FTSE 100 opens firm , chartists predict 5 , 000 . Britain ' s leading share index powered higher at Thursday ' s open and was on track to top the 5 , 000 - point level , boosted by record closing highs in London and New York and early strength in financial stocks , dealers said . At 0749 GMT , the FTSE 100 traded 27 . 6 points higher at 4 , 991 . 8 , matching its all - time best hit on Wednesday . Technical analysts predicted a move to above 5 , 000 , with minor resistance following at 5 , 020 . 
